{"id":54550,"title":"Diurnal body temperature rise is reduced in diabetes with autonomic neuropathy.","abstract":"We conducted a retrospective study of 60 patients with ischemic heart disease (31 with diabetes and 29 without diabetes) to investigate the impact of diabetes on diurnal body temperature patterns. We found that the increase of axillary body temperature in the evening was reduced in the presence of diabetes, which was associated with autonomic neuropathy.","date":"2014-03-26","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24452371","annotations":[{"name":"Diabetes mellitus","weight":0.814954,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diabetes_mellitus"},{"name":"Ischaemic heart disease","weight":0.78496,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ischaemic_heart_disease"},{"name":"Autonomic nervous system","weight":0.778467,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Autonomic_nervous_system"},{"name":"Heart disease","weight":0.775701,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heart_disease"},{"name":"Peripheral neuropathy","weight":0.772383,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peripheral_neuropathy"},{"name":"Thermoregulation","weight":0.741014,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thermoregulation"},{"name":"Heart","weight":0.738937,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heart"},{"name":"Ischemia","weight":0.70749,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ischemia"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.705743,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Dysautonomia","weight":0.448198,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dysautonomia"},{"name":"Temperature","weight":0.385461,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Temperature"},{"name":"Retrospective cohort study","weight":0.135948,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Retrospective_cohort_study"},{"name":"Diurnality","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diurnality"},{"name":"Axilla","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Axilla"}]}
